properties.store_name: Our City Farm (Villarreal Family Farm, LLC)
properties.description: Our City Farm is owned and operated by the Villarreal family in the heart of St. Louis. This urban farm produces Certified Naturally Grown pastured poultry, farm fresh eggs, and a variety of herbs and heirloom produce. Our City Farm is a repurposed, once-vancant lot in St. Louis City that is now a vibrant and thriving urban farm. Our City Farm produces hyper-local, fresh, heirloom and exotic produce to the community in the form of an extended CSA that runs for 6 months out of the year. Our City Farm uses simple, traditional farming techniques along with sustainable practices. Their goal is to increase their sustainability and they have designed their farm as such.
